videos.headline: Nebraska RB dives for end zone on 18-yard TD
videos.description: Devine Ozigbo finds a hole and stretches for the pylon, giving the Cornhuskers an early lead over the Boilermakers.

videos.headline: Purdue RB goes airborne to set up TD
videos.description: D.J. Knox shows off his vertical by leaping over a Nebraska defender for a 13-yard gain, leading to a Boilermaker touchdown.

videos.headline: Nebraska punter slips and takes a tumble
videos.description: Caleb Lightbourn loses his footing on a punt as he falls to the turf and gives Purdue great field position.

videos.headline: Purdue QB on target for 12-yard TD
videos.description: David Blough connects with a wide-open Brycen Hopkins, who walks into the end zone to extend the Boilermakers' lead to 27-7.

videos.headline: Nebraska trims lead with 21-yard TD pass
videos.description: Adrian Martinez finds WR JD Spielman down the sideline, who makes a man miss and cuts the Purdue lead to 27-14.

videos.headline: Purdue answers with 6-yard TD run
videos.description: D.J. Knox spins off a tackle and powers his way to the end zone to make 35-14 Boilermakers.

videos.headline: Martinez throws dime for 21-yard TD
videos.description: Adrian Martinez makes a perfect 21-yard touchdown pass to JD Spielman, keeping Nebraska in the game and cutting the lead to 35-21.

videos.headline: Purdue RB overpowers defender for 6-yard TD
videos.description: Markell Jones runs downhill and gets to the end zone, putting Purdue's lead back at 21 points, 42-21.

videos.headline: Nebraska hangs around with 23-yard TD
videos.description: RB Devine Ozigbo slips out of tackles and takes the sideline all the way to the end zone, making it 42-28 Purdue.
